{"tid":594381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 強國豆腐渣工程，天橋塌下，多人傷亡","createTime":"2018-03-15T19:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T22:57:17.000Z","uid":130105,"like":28,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"4a183159c00fa2efde150da141f1ee871fabfab0","tid":594381,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:23:51.000Z","msg":"美國都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">BREAKING NEWS: 'Multiple deaths' as 950-ton pedestrian bridge collapses on top of cars and people on Florida college campus just days after it was installed</span><br />\n<br />\n&bull;Pedestrian bridge linking two parts of Florida International University campus collapsed on Thursday<br />\n&bull;The 950-ton bridge was installed last Saturday and had not yet been open to pedestrian traffic<br />\n&bull;Police say there are 'multiple deaths' as well as a number of cars and motorists trapped underneath the rubble <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/15/18/4A3A7EB300000578-5506597-image-a-55_1521139353728.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F18%2F4A3A7EB300000578-5506597-image-a-55_1521139353728.jpg&h=52e755fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/15/18/4A3A866100000578-5506597-image-a-61_1521139763439.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F18%2F4A3A866100000578-5506597-image-a-61_1521139763439.jpg&h=5f5fcb17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Television images captured from helicopter show numerous cars that were crushed by the weight of the bridge<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/15/18/4A3A7EA600000578-5506597-image-a-56_1521139358880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F18%2F4A3A7EA600000578-5506597-image-a-56_1521139358880.jpg&h=77f70090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Images show a number of emergency rescue workers crawling along the rubble in an attempt to spot survivors<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/15/18/4A3A742100000578-5506597-The_bridge_which_was_installed_last_Saturday_morning_was_built_t-m-59_1521139476259.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F18%2F4A3A742100000578-5506597-The_bridge_which_was_installed_last_Saturday_morning_was_built_t-m-59_1521139476259.jpg&h=fbb0d0e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The bridge, which was installed last Saturday morning, was built to provide pedestrian access from FIU&rsquo;s main campus to an area that houses a number of student residences<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/15/18/4A3A741100000578-5506597-The_950_ton_span_which_was_built_over_Tamiami_Trail_was_not_yet_-m-60_1521139508611.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F18%2F4A3A741100000578-5506597-The_950_ton_span_which_was_built_over_Tamiami_Trail_was_not_yet_-m-60_1521139508611.jpg&h=3b38d432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The 950-ton span, which was built over Tamiami Trail, was not yet open to pedestrians<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/15/19/4A3A8E3A00000578-5506597-image-a-64_1521140500668.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F19%2F4A3A8E3A00000578-5506597-image-a-64_1521140500668.jpg&h=97485a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The image above shows a victim being wheeled away from the scene of the collapsed bridge<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/15/19/4A3A8E4200000578-5506597-image-a-65_1521140509184.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F19%2F4A3A8E4200000578-5506597-image-a-65_1521140509184.jpg&h=9badfa7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Emergency crews load a victim into a waiting ambulance at the scene<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/15/18/4A3A8A6D00000578-5506597-image-a-63_1521139952780.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F18%2F4A3A8A6D00000578-5506597-image-a-63_1521139952780.jpg&h=9b456854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/03/15/19/4A3A6DFD00000578-5506597-image-a-67_1521141006778.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F19%2F4A3A6DFD00000578-5506597-image-a-67_1521141006778.jpg&h=4f76f3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Rescue workers frantically search for survivors as they stand atop the rubble of the pedestrian bridge<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/03/15/4327142866611291106/1024x576_MP4_4327142866611291106.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F4327142866611291106%2F1024x576_MP4_4327142866611291106.mp4&d=XAG6UsVC1C%2FKdYYBU0ASQ%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=bb42f9aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/03/15/4327142866611291106/1024x576_MP4_4327142866611291106.mp4</a><br />\n Pedestrian bridge in Florida collapses, trapping cars underneath<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/03/15/8461928287225428991/1024x576_MP4_8461928287225428991.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F8461928287225428991%2F1024x576_MP4_8461928287225428991.mp4&d=XAG6UsVC1C%2FKdYYBU0ASQ%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6dc65174\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/03/15/8461928287225428991/1024x576_MP4_8461928287225428991.mp4</a><br />\n Bridge collapses onto road at Florida International University<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5506597/Pedestrian-bridge-collapses-cars-people-campus.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-5506597%2FPedestrian-bridge-collapses-cars-people-campus.html&d=XAG6UsVC1C%2FKdYYBU0ASQ%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=7146b91a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-5506597/Pedestrian-bridge-collapses-cars-people-campus.html</a>"},{"pid":"9dc9b202ed799504b64cb2f8a81c2e7ecab5a062","tid":594381,"uid":13541,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b775ce531eb9398b81b6b00f6df9c67a5473289","tid":594381,"uid":33463,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e32df719a1f56e937f7c839e054ba7181fbfdde","tid":594381,"uid":45368,"like":21,"dislike":7,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:35:33.000Z","msg":"連登仔：實係MIC支那製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43febe253668b034f54118892e659ec8b08fd80","tid":594381,"uid":17765,"like":73,"dislike":11,"score":62,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T19:36:27.000Z","msg":"標題黨好好玩？"},{"pid":"24c6cfa1b