？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T00:35:01.000Z","msg":"美國唔係強國？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511ccb799ff4f7e33e9df6c5e44a1f5b4589a414","tid":594381,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T00:37:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fca315a2a1f377363e4e1df1dbf010e21360c21a","tid":594381,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T00:41:39.000Z","msg":"Here are some, as outlined by the university:<br />\n<br />\nIt was designed to withstand a Category 5 hurricane.<br />\n<br />\nIts durability was supposed to exceed 100 years.<br />\n<br />\nIt's the first bridge in the world to be constructed entirely of self-cleaning concrete: It's made of titanium dioxide which, when exposed to sunlight, captures pollutant particles from the air and cleans its own concrete surfaces.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\nIt was installed in just a few hours just five days ago, although its construction wasn't finished.</span><br />\n<br />\nThe main span was built nearby to avoid traffic interruption and moved using a state-of-the-art, computer-controlled system that carried and set the 950-ton section. It's called Self-Propelled Modular Transportation and this was the largest pedestrian bridge in US history to be moved using this method.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2018/03/15/us/fiu-pedestrian-bridge-stats-trnd/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2Fus%2Ffiu-pedestrian-bridge-stats-trnd%2Findex.html&d=XAG6UsVC1C%2FKdYYBU0ASQ%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=f03a5ad8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2Fus%2Ffiu-pedestrian-bridge-stats-trnd%2Findex.html&h=9d2153ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2018/03/15/us/fiu-pedestrian-bridge-stats-trnd/index.html